Quintin Sondergaard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quintin_Sondergaard 0 Quentin Charles Sondergaard, known primarily as Quintin Sondergaard (January 11, 1925 – February 15, 1984), was an American actor principally active on television westerns from 1957-70. He had a supporting role with eleven appearances as "Deputy Quint" on the series Tombstone Territory, with co-stars Pat Conway, Richard Eastham, and Gilman Rankin. Tombstone Territory began in 1957 on ABC and then switched to syndication in 1959.
